_sText: UPDATED TO SURF_CONCISE_V3 Fixed some bugs and removed a ramp from the top platfors. Looks more smooth now. Also fixed some small ramp bugs. :::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::: Nice and Smooth surf map. I added 40 spawns, but a 10 on 10 game would have been nice.
